00:38:14.480 --> 00:38:17.260
and actually I had
colleagues from all

00:38:17.260 --> 00:38:20.880
over the world that
had some ideas here.

00:38:20.880 --> 00:38:22.930
How could Google
help save the Ocean?

00:38:22.930 --> 00:38:26.140
What do we do with data now?

